#, fuzzy
msgid "We're going to do a deep dive into the https://github.com/a2aproject/a2a-samples/tree/main/samples/python/hosts/content_creation[Content Creation] sample from the https://github.com/a2aproject/a2a-samples[a2a-samples] project."
msgstr "Vamos nos aprofundar na amostra link:https://github.com/a2aproject/a2a-samples/tree/main/samples/python/hosts/content_creation[Content Creation] do projeto link:https://github.com/a2aproject/a2a-samples[a2a-samples] ."

#. type: Plain text
